130
00:14:07,740 --> 00:14:10,330
SPEAKER_24: The game's not over yet!

139
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:43,000
SPEAKER_24: - Sit.
- Just one more round!

140
00:14:44,779 --> 00:14:47,769
SPEAKER_24: I am very sorry, but you've got nothing left.

141
00:14:48,049 --> 00:14:51,779
SPEAKER_24: What could you stake the bet on?
We don't accept empty bets.

142
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,340
SPEAKER_24: I'll stake my life.

143
00:14:53,419 --> 00:14:56,480
SPEAKER_24: Don't talk like that.

144
00:14:56,549 --> 00:15:00,220
SPEAKER_24: Anyway, your life's worth little now.

146
00:15:03,730 --> 00:15:06,529
SPEAKER_24: We'll formalize the transfer in a few days...

147
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:08,289
SPEAKER_24: and explain to your old man.

313
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,460
SPEAKER_24: So, no running?

501
00:58:25,789 --> 00:58:27,420
SPEAKER_24: This is too much.

800
01:30:02,989 --> 01:30:04,619
SPEAKER_24: There's trouble at your home.

801
01:30:04,689 --> 01:30:07,390
SPEAKER_24: Red Guards are swarming over the place.

822
01:31:36,520 --> 01:31:38,449
SPEAKER_24: We must be going.

826
01:31:51,670 --> 01:31:53,659
SPEAKER_24: Erxi is good with his hands.

827
01:31:53,739 --> 01:31:56,930
SPEAKER_24: He painted all the Chairman Maos
in our factory!

829
01:32:01,979 --> 01:32:04,810
SPEAKER_24: Thanks, we'll go to the factory bathhouse.

830
01:32:10,619 --> 01:32:12,920
SPEAKER_24: You've gone to so much trouble.

863
01:36:16,430 --> 01:36:17,989
SPEAKER_24: Chairman Mao...

864
01:36:18,869 --> 01:36:21,600
SPEAKER_24: Comrade Fengxia's mine now.

897
01:40:04,689 --> 01:40:06,279
SPEAKER_24: Dad! Mom!

1042
01:50:52,210 --> 01:50:54,829
SPEAKER_24: Do as Mommy says and push.

1043
01:50:54,909 --> 01:50:56,640
SPEAKER_24: Everything will be fine.

1075
01:53:19,020 --> 01:53:22,050
SPEAKER_24: This is the same Wang Bin
who once insulted...

1078
01:53:31,029 --> 01:53:33,159
SPEAKER_24: We dragged him here today...

1079
01:53:33,300 --> 01:53:36,270
SPEAKER_24: to educate him, to criticize him...

1080
01:53:37,340 --> 01:53:39,899
SPEAKER_24: and to let him witness her giving birth.

1159
01:59:37,760 --> 01:59:40,890
SPEAKER_24: My son was only 5.5 pounds.

1195
02:02:18,619 --> 02:02:20,680
SPEAKER_24: Never mind. Drag him over!

1196
02:02:21,489 --> 02:02:23,720
SPEAKER_24: She's bleeding! Quick!

1253
02:07:11,979 --> 02:07:13,350
SPEAKER_24: It's okay.

